robot - package robot
Contains code related to robot functionality.
robot.acuators - package robot.acuators
Contains "fancy" wrapper classes for motors and other actuators.
robot.behavior - package robot.behavior
Contains "behavior" classes for the robot.
robot.control - package robot.control
Classes used for robot control.
robot.logic - package robot.logic
Logic classes do not directly manipulate actuators; instead, they perform logic necessary to robot functionality and make calls to corresponding behavior classes.
robot.logic.auton - package robot.logic.auton
Contains classes related to the autonomous phase of the robot's logic.
robot.logic.climb - package robot.logic.climb
Contains classes related to climbing logic.
robot.logic.teleop - package robot.logic.teleop
Contains classes related to logic during the teleoperated period of the game.
robot.sensors - package robot.sensors
Contains various "fancy" wrappers for sensors in addition to a catalog of static sensor instances.
